com.cloudera.api.model

Class ApiActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.api.model.ApiActivity

  • public class ApiActivity
extends Object
    Represents a user activity, such as a MapReduce job, a Hive query, an Oozie workflow, etc.
